pageProduct.name: Swisse Vitamin C + Probiotic Chewable 60 Chewable Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

SWISSE ULTIBOOST VITAMIN C + PROBIOTIC CHEWABLE is a premium quality, great tasting formula providing 1,000 mg of vitamin C and 1 billion CFU of Bacillus oagulans, a fridge-free probiotic, per daily dose.

Warnings

Not suitable for children. Bacillus coagulans may affect the way some medicines work, including immunosuppressants. Consult your health professional before taking with other medicines.

For adult use only.

 

Common Uses

Antioxidant Support: Vitamin C provides antioxidant support to help reduce free radicals formed in the body, and maintains general health and wellbeing.

Common Cold Symptom Relief: Vitamin C helps reduce the duration and severity of common cold symptoms.

Immune Health: Vitamin C supports a healthy immune system and function.

Ingredients

Vitamin C (ascorbic acid)  250 mg
Vitamin C (ascorbic acid from sodium ascorbate)  250 mg
Total Vitamin C 500 mg 
Bacillus coagulans (MTCC No. 5260) (Unique IS2™)    500 million CFU

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Chew two tablets daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. Do not swallow whole.
